nodes.bodyText:
@stefnotch Thanks. I'm sorry but I don't understand the new document addition. quarkus-keycloak-authorization is to support the OIDC service applications only when (as per your PR, Keycloak does the policy-driven authorization). If one has an OIDC web-app application which your PR links to then this quarkus-keycloak-authorization will not be activated.
This is why I'm confused about the message of this PR. Perhaps I'm missing the point :-), please clarify. CC @pedroigor
Thanks
